The files in this directory have mixed licensing:

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
rsem-generate-data-matrix
rsem-generate-data-matrix-counts
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
These scripts are derived from RSEM (RNA-Seq by Expectation-Maximization)
by Bo Li and Colin Dewey, and are licensed under the GNU General Public
License v3.0 (GPL-3.0).

Modifications were made by Wendy Demos (RGD, Medical College of Wisconsin)
in August 2024 to use File::Basename for cleaner output column headers and
to output TPM values (rsem-generate-data-matrix) and expected counts
(rsem-generate-data-matrix-counts) respectively.

Original RSEM source: https://github.com/deweylab/RSEM
GPL-3.0 license text: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
fastq_screen.conf
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This file is a configuration template created for this pipeline and is
licensed under the MIT License (see the repository root LICENSE file).
